1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,961
♪Love's little quiz
takes seven parts sweet♪

2
00:00:10,962 --> 00:00:13,559
♪And three parts bitter,
till you and I meet♪

3
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:17,159
♪I pretend I'm not there,
but secretly stay♪

4
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:26,399
♪Waiting for you♪

5
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:31,400
♪We've got so many
romantic dreams to unfold♪

6
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:36,224
♪Finally hearing
the I love you I long to hold♪

7
00:00:36,225 --> 00:00:39,839
♪Falling fast
into the swirl of your eyes♪

8
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,399
♪It's just too tempting, so tempting♪

9
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,499
♪Never could I have guessed♪

10
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:46,499
♪My heart's rhythm♪

11
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,632
♪How beautiful it is, meeting you♪

12
00:01:02,975 --> 00:01:05,961
=Late to Love=
(Adapted from "My Husband Is A Billionaire!")

13
00:01:05,962 --> 00:01:09,100
=Episode 24=

14
00:01:09,419 --> 00:01:11,459
You want to beat me
fair and square for once?

15
00:01:12,820 --> 00:01:14,099
I'll give you that chance.

16
00:01:15,619 --> 00:01:16,980
Let's make a bet.

17
00:01:17,300 --> 00:01:18,340
How about it?

18
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:23,420
Sure.

19
00:01:24,139 --> 00:01:25,260
What are we betting on?

20
00:01:25,619 --> 00:01:27,500
You love Xu Nange, right?

21
00:01:27,979 --> 00:01:30,659
This whole thing started because of her.

22
00:01:30,699 --> 00:01:31,900
So today,

23
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:33,459
let's use her

24
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:35,379
to put an end to all of this.

25
00:01:39,737 --> 00:01:42,057
(Ye Group)

26
00:01:51,699 --> 00:01:53,579
You came by yourself?

27
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,299
You've got some nerve.

28
00:01:55,499 --> 00:01:57,138
This might be your turf,

29
00:01:57,139 --> 00:01:58,939
but it's not like you're above the law.

30
00:02:01,499 --> 00:02:02,939
I brought what you wanted.

31
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:04,340
The encrypted flash drive.

32
00:02:07,219 --> 00:02:11,139
Looks like Huo Zichen
actually got the job done this time.

33
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,098
Look at you,

34
00:02:13,099 --> 00:02:14,179
coming all this way

35
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:15,699
just to hand over

36
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:17,739
your life's work to me.

37
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:19,580
You can never beat me.

38
00:02:21,059 --> 00:02:22,220
Where is Huo Beiyan?

39
00:02:24,559 --> 00:02:25,899
A low-life parasite who can barely

40
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:28,739
stand on her own two feet
without Huo Beiyan

41
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:31,620
doesn't get to come in here
and negotiate with me.

42
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,379
Low-life?

43
00:02:34,779 --> 00:02:35,699
Is that all a person

44
00:02:35,700 --> 00:02:37,220
is worth to you?

45
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:39,058
Just their identity,

46
00:02:39,059 --> 00:02:40,058
their wealth,

47
00:02:40,059 --> 00:02:41,500
and their social status?

48
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:42,938
Of course.

49
00:02:42,939 --> 00:02:46,019
Don't tell me it's honesty, kindness,

50
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:47,218
or hard work.

51
00:02:47,219 --> 00:02:50,938
Those are just fairy tales
poor people tell themselves to feel better.

52
00:02:50,939 --> 00:02:52,859
The only things that actually matter

53
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:55,859
are the walls built by money and power.

54
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:58,139
And compared to those walls,

55
00:02:58,140 --> 00:03:00,060
you're just a speck of dust.

56
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:06,939
Ye Xin, you're honestly pathetic.

57
00:03:08,539 --> 00:03:11,939
You lost everything,
so stop talking big.

58
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:16,419
Want to hear Huo Beiyan's voice

59
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:18,340
one last time?

60
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:23,818
Take care of Huo Beiyan.

61
00:03:23,819 --> 00:03:24,938
Leave no loose ends.

62
00:03:24,939 --> 00:03:25,618
Ye Xin,

63
00:03:25,619 --> 00:03:27,538
this is the Linhai Police Department.

64
00:03:27,539 --> 00:03:29,859
You're under suspicion
for manufacturing banned substances.

65
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,979
You're officially under arrest.

66
00:03:35,740 --> 00:03:37,600
Ye Xin, there's solid evidence
against your company

67
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,680
for making counterfeit drugs.

68
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,590
We're placing you under arrest
according to the law.

69
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,539
Wait, no.

70
00:03:41,619 --> 00:03:42,498
It wasn't me.

71
00:03:42,499 --> 00:03:44,859
- I didn't. You have the wrong person.
- Move.

72
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:47,058
Let me go!

73
00:03:47,059 --> 00:03:49,019
- Take her away.
- You've got the wrong person!

74
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,259
Xu Nange,

75
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:52,060
just you wait!

76
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,139
Are you alright, Mrs. Huo?

77
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,220
Where is Huo Beiyan?

78
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:55,899
Don't worry.

79
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:58,340
Everything is under Mr. Huo's control.

80
00:04:01,099 --> 00:04:02,378
So you're saying

81
00:04:02,379 --> 00:04:04,379
Huo Beiyan already knew I'd come here?

82
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,498
Please

83
00:04:12,499 --> 00:04:14,579
come back with us
to assist with the investigation.

84
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:16,259
Since you're turning yourself in,

85
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,699
make sure you cooperate fully

86
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:20,019
and explain everything
from start to finish.

87
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:21,939
It'll help get your sentence reduced.

88
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,299
Okay.

89
00:04:23,380 --> 00:04:25,059
I'll cooperate.

90
00:04:25,739 --> 00:04:26,699
Mr. Huo,

91
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:29,099
could you also come by the station
to give a statement?

92
00:04:31,219 --> 00:04:32,140
Take him away.

93
00:04:39,539 --> 00:04:40,778
I'm betting that Xu Nange

94
00:04:40,779 --> 00:04:42,020
loves me.

95
00:04:44,299 --> 00:04:46,178
Once she finds out I'm abducted,

96
00:04:46,179 --> 00:04:48,739
she'll do whatever it takes to save me.

97
00:04:48,779 --> 00:04:50,778
She'll hand over
the evidence she cares about

98
00:04:50,779 --> 00:04:51,978
more than life itself to Ye Xin

99
00:04:51,979 --> 00:04:53,580
just to buy my safety.

100
00:05:02,339 --> 00:05:03,820
If I win,

101
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:06,780
you turn yourself in
and testify against Ye Xin.

102
00:05:08,460 --> 00:05:09,979
Give the Huo family

103
00:05:10,099 --> 00:05:11,739
one last shred of dignity.

104
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,179
Are you in?

105
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:14,820
Sure.

106
00:05:16,219 --> 00:05:18,340
But what if you lose?

107
00:05:25,099 --> 00:05:26,539
I'll end it myself.

108
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,419
I won't dirty your hands.

109
00:05:29,539 --> 00:05:30,659
Deal.

110
00:05:50,060 --> 00:05:51,738
I brought what you wanted.

111
00:05:51,739 --> 00:05:53,099
The encrypted flash drive.

112
00:06:05,979 --> 00:06:07,059
Zichen.

113
00:06:07,820 --> 00:06:09,900
Your opponent was never me.

114
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:13,979
It was always yourself.

115
00:06:14,380 --> 00:06:15,580
Get it?

116
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:27,536
♪Did I, did I♪

117
00:06:27,537 --> 00:06:30,320
♪So she said♪

118
00:06:34,287 --> 00:06:39,036
♪Smile, I try♪

119
00:06:39,037 --> 00:06:44,670
♪To build it on my own♪

120
00:06:45,250 --> 00:06:51,157
♪Never could have seen,
never could have dream♪

121
00:06:51,337 --> 00:06:56,457
♪All the while you know,
it's all for show♪

122
00:06:58,739 --> 00:06:59,940
(Zichen.)

123
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:03,260
(I hope this long sentence)

124
00:07:03,659 --> 00:07:05,739
(will finally make you see
the error of your ways.)

125
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:26,695
♪You bolt and call it home♪

126
00:07:30,312 --> 00:07:38,645
♪You saved it, we made it home♪

127
00:07:44,739 --> 00:07:46,059
She's out.

128
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:47,059
Miss Ye.

129
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,499
Dr. X's paper

130
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:49,858
was officially published online.

131
00:07:49,859 --> 00:07:52,658
It points out that your company's NIT-33,
developed to treat Alzheimer's,

132
00:07:52,659 --> 00:07:53,978
is actually highly toxic

133
00:07:53,979 --> 00:07:55,298
to humans.

134
00:07:55,299 --> 00:07:56,778
Have you seen that paper?

135
00:07:56,779 --> 00:07:58,340
What's your take on this?

136
00:07:58,900 --> 00:07:59,780
Miss Ye.

137
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:16,179
What are you looking at?

138
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:17,900
You look so upset.

139
00:08:19,099 --> 00:08:21,499
See, Huo Group
still got dragged into this.

140
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:23,260
Look at how bad the stock is crashing.

141
00:08:23,539 --> 00:08:24,739
So what?

142
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:28,780
Didn't you say everything
was under control?

143
00:08:30,859 --> 00:08:32,899
It'll bounce back eventually.

144
00:08:36,740 --> 00:08:37,778
Come on.

145
00:08:37,779 --> 00:08:39,060
Stop worrying.

146
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:41,099
After all, NIT-33

147
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:43,099
was a joint venture
between our companies.

148
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:46,540
It's natural that Huo Group takes a hit
now that Ye Group has gone under.

149
00:08:46,699 --> 00:08:47,538
I've run the numbers.

150
00:08:47,539 --> 00:08:49,340
It's really just

151
00:08:49,459 --> 00:08:50,820
a minor financial loss.

152
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:53,340
How is that a minor loss?

153
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:55,259
Your grandma
built this company from scratch,

154
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:57,779
and it's the life's work
of three generations of your family.

155
00:08:58,020 --> 00:09:00,499
Besides, you guys were actually
the victims in all of this.

156
00:09:02,299 --> 00:09:03,778
Grandma always says

157
00:09:03,779 --> 00:09:05,859
every cloud has a silver lining.

158
00:09:10,659 --> 00:09:12,099
Alright, stop stressing over it.

159
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,339
Let's go.

160
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:15,058
Time to head home.

161
00:09:15,059 --> 00:09:16,420
Don't keep everyone waiting.

162
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:21,180
As everyone knows,

163
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:22,979
our family

164
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:25,259
has been going through
a bit of a rough patch lately.

165
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:28,418
Because of that,
Nange and Beiyan's wedding

166
00:09:28,419 --> 00:09:30,420
can't be the massive, lavish affair

167
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,060
we originally planned.

168
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,460
This family dinner

169
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:36,818
will serve

170
00:09:36,819 --> 00:09:38,619
as a small, intimate wedding for them.

171
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,259
Nange, Beiyan,

172
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:41,979
I hope you won't hold it against me.

173
00:09:42,980 --> 00:09:45,818
Sure, it’s a bit low-key,

174
00:09:45,819 --> 00:09:47,460
but I put my whole heart

175
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:49,220
into it.

176
00:09:50,659 --> 00:09:51,379
Dad,

177
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:52,580
we know.

178
00:09:55,299 --> 00:09:56,099
Alright.

179
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,460
I'll take the first toast.

180
00:10:00,939 --> 00:10:01,779
Dad,

181
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:04,700
maybe a few years in jail will actually

182
00:10:04,779 --> 00:10:05,899
do Zichen some good.

183
00:10:06,539 --> 00:10:07,779
Don't worry.

184
00:10:08,779 --> 00:10:11,340
Every cloud has a silver lining, right?

185
00:10:14,659 --> 00:10:16,019
Nange,

186
00:10:16,299 --> 00:10:17,379
I'm handing Beiyan

187
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:18,578
over to you now.

188
00:10:18,579 --> 00:10:19,499
He's got

189
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,339
a stubborn streak,

190
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:22,420
and he can be real pigheaded sometimes.

191
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:25,180
But

192
00:10:25,740 --> 00:10:27,139
don't hold back on my account.

193
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:28,298
Call him out when he's wrong,

194
00:10:28,299 --> 00:10:29,540
and keep him in line.

195
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:32,820
Okay.

196
00:10:33,659 --> 00:10:35,578
Knowing you're in Nange's corner

197
00:10:35,579 --> 00:10:37,180
makes me feel a lot better.

198
00:10:37,579 --> 00:10:38,619
But

199
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:39,859
I still have to ask Beiyan

200
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:41,938
to look after Nange.

201
00:10:41,939 --> 00:10:43,058
Once she

202
00:10:43,059 --> 00:10:44,339
gets into the lab,

203
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:45,818
she tunes out the rest of the world.

204
00:10:45,819 --> 00:10:48,060
Don't you mind
the Huo family's current situation?

205
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:51,379
A rich man's drop is a poor man's flood.

206
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:54,859
You shouldn't be saying that.

207
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,499
Nange,

208
00:11:03,819 --> 00:11:05,060
this

209
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,619
is a family heirloom

210
00:11:06,659 --> 00:11:09,180
passed down through generations.

211
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:13,420
Its last owner

212
00:11:13,779 --> 00:11:15,619
was Beiyan's mother.

213
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,180
Today,

214
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:22,139
I'm passing it on to you.

215
00:11:22,699 --> 00:11:23,619
Take it.

216
00:11:28,740 --> 00:11:29,859
Thank you, Dad.

217
00:11:32,699 --> 00:11:35,099
I'll do everything I can
to cure Grandma.

218
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:36,300
Good.

219
00:11:36,539 --> 00:11:37,739
I believe in you.

220
00:11:38,225 --> 00:11:41,099
♪Why don't you take me too?♪

221
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:41,938
Come on.

222
00:11:41,939 --> 00:11:44,580
Let's all raise a glass.

223
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:48,099
Cheers to the newlyweds.

224
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:50,899
Cheers.

225
00:11:51,850 --> 00:11:57,095
♪I could take you in♪

226
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:07,139
Before we head to Europe,

227
00:12:07,140 --> 00:12:08,938
interested in extending

228
00:12:08,939 --> 00:12:10,180
the contract first?

229
00:12:14,779 --> 00:12:16,578
I found a new breakthrough

230
00:12:16,579 --> 00:12:17,859
for Alzheimer's.

231
00:12:22,579 --> 00:12:24,979
Why are elderly people less likely

232
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:27,298
to develop reversible amnesia
than younger people?

233
00:12:27,299 --> 00:12:28,178
I think it has

234
00:12:28,179 --> 00:12:30,460
everything to do with hormones.

235
00:12:32,659 --> 00:12:33,938
So,

236
00:12:33,939 --> 00:12:35,619
you're going to help me run

237
00:12:35,620 --> 00:12:36,778
a control experiment tonight,

238
00:12:36,779 --> 00:12:40,019
analyzing sex hormone secretion levels.

239
00:12:40,939 --> 00:12:43,259
Wait, what hormones?

240
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:56,820
Are you ready?

241
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:58,739
Our experiment

242
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:00,540
is about to begin.

243
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:07,770
♪Corner cafe, same wooden chairs♪

244
00:13:08,787 --> 00:13:14,995
♪You walked in
like you were still there♪

245
00:13:15,699 --> 00:13:17,019
Xu Nange,

246
00:13:17,539 --> 00:13:19,019
you're nervous too, aren't you?

247
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:26,219
♪After all this time,
after all the while♪

248
00:13:26,220 --> 00:13:27,420
Don't talk.

249
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:29,499
Tonight

250
00:13:29,779 --> 00:13:32,340
is the perfect chance
for our experiment.

251
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:41,932
♪Just staring at the ghost
that's stepping right up♪

252
00:13:59,125 --> 00:14:02,899
♪What destiny brought us to meet♪

253
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:06,220
♪Two different worlds, a love so sweet♪

254
00:14:06,225 --> 00:14:09,599
♪A wish we made
in a past life, it seems♪

255
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:12,454
♪Destined to cross time and dream ♪

256
00:14:12,455 --> 00:14:16,295
♪Like a fairytale story told♪

257
00:14:16,375 --> 00:14:19,632
♪A gentle breeze feels so bold♪

258
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:23,336
♪As your hair brushes past your ear♪

259
00:14:23,337 --> 00:14:25,694
♪I long to kiss your cheek, my dear♪

260
00:14:25,695 --> 00:14:29,934
♪All my longing, all my love for you♪

261
00:14:29,935 --> 00:14:32,495
♪Has never changed, it's forever true♪

262
00:14:32,937 --> 00:14:39,335
♪It's the hand of fate
that we meet again♪

263
00:14:40,137 --> 00:14:44,575
♪Let me hold you once again♪

264
00:14:44,825 --> 00:14:47,745
♪Resting against your chest♪

265
00:14:48,095 --> 00:14:53,336
♪Your warmth shines like stars at night♪

266
00:14:53,337 --> 00:14:58,136
♪Let me kiss you once again♪

267
00:14:58,137 --> 00:15:00,936
♪No reason needed♪

268
00:15:00,937 --> 00:15:03,134
♪My heart belongs to you♪

269
00:15:03,135 --> 00:15:08,855
♪I'm not afraid
to cross time to find you♪
